have you ever visited mexico write your comments i'm a mexican girl i recomended my country here we have delicious food beautiful women and handsome men and wonderful places i have been to mexico many times i found that the farther away from the united states you go the better it is the border towns are dirty and crime ridden and exist to cater to the tourists my visit to mexico city and the areas around it was fantastic the people were warm and friendly we never felt like we were in danger and really had a great time i also visited the yucatan peninsula to visit the ancient ruins and do some skin diving it was excellent again the people were friendly and did much more than we expected for us i would visit mexico again and again if it were possible he sido a m xico muchas veces encontr que el m s lejano lejos de los estados unidos que usted va mejor es las ciudades de la frontera es sucio y crimen montado y existe para abastecer a los turistas mi visita a ciudad de m xico y a las reas alrededor de ella era fant stica la gente era caliente y amistosa nunca nos sent amos como est bamos en peligro y realmente ten amos un gran rato tambi n visit la pen nsula de yucatan para visitar las ruinas antiguas y para hacer un cierto salto de la piel era excelente la gente era amistosa e hizo otra vez mucho m s que esperamos para nosotros visitar a m xico repetidas veces si era posible Spanish grammar Spanish pronouns Origin of the name California Spanish verbs Goya Awards Bleed Like Me Mexico Spanish determiners Spanish prepositions Mexican-American War Vicente Fern__ndez Mexico City Yucat__n Cuisine of Argentina Mexican Federal District Romance copula Hispanic Luis Bu__uel Spanish dialects and varieties Mexico City International Airport Mexico (state) Naucalpan Tourism in Mexico Jorge Casta__eda Joaquin Murietta Spanish nouns Mecano Thalia Sodi Geography of Mexico Politics of Mexico Chichen Itza Mexican rock Madrid Index of political parties Chabacano language Spanish in the Un